@startuml
actor Client
participant IndividualsAPI
participant TransactionService
participant WalletService
participant Kafka
participant TransactionServiceConsumer
participant DB

== Инициализация вывода ==

Client -> IndividualsAPI: POST /transactions/withdrawal/init
IndividualsAPI -> TransactionService: calc withdrawal conditions
TransactionService -> WalletService: проверка баланса

alt Баланс достаточен
    WalletService --> TransactionService: OK, лимиты
    TransactionService --> IndividualsAPI: условия вывода
    IndividualsAPI --> Client: 200 OK + условия вывода
else Баланс недостаточен
    WalletService --> TransactionService: ERROR
    TransactionService --> IndividualsAPI: 402 Payment Required
    IndividualsAPI --> Client: 402 Payment Required
end

== Подтверждение вывода ==

Client -> IndividualsAPI: POST /transactions/withdrawal/confirm
IndividualsAPI -> TransactionService: confirm withdrawal
TransactionService -> DB: создать транзакцию PENDING
TransactionService -> Kafka: WithdrawalRequested
TransactionService --> IndividualsAPI: PENDING, transactionId
IndividualsAPI --> Client: 202 Accepted, PENDING, transactionId

== Асинхронная обработка ==


TransactionServiceConsumer -> WalletService: списать средства

alt Списание успешно
    WalletService -> DB: Баланс--
    WalletService --> TransactionServiceConsumer: OK
    TransactionServiceConsumer -> DB: статус транзакции COMPLETED
else Ошибка списания
    WalletService --> TransactionServiceConsumer: ERROR
    TransactionServiceConsumer -> DB: статус транзакции FAILED\n+ причина ошибки
    TransactionServiceConsumer -> Kafka: WithdrawalFailed\n(для уведомлений)
end
@enduml